{"title":"想起亲人在边疆","authors":["张永枚"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":7,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起亲人在边疆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张永枚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六月的太阳火一样亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蝉儿也躲到树叶下乘凉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听见蝉儿“知了知了”地唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起亲人在边疆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他站在发烫的岩石上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳晒枯了绿叶的伪装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水淋淋他也不揩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两手紧紧端着枪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿变成一朵云彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给他遮住六月的阳光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿变成清凉的微风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹干他那汗湿的军装。……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六月的雷声滚在天上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浓密的雨雾遮住了远方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨点飘在我的窗户上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起亲人在边疆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披着风雨巡逻在边防，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨过暴风折断的白杨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪电照亮了每一道深谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机警的眼睛比闪电还亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿迎着狂风暴雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻过重重叠叠的山岗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去到亲人驻守的边疆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给他送去爱情的力量！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1956，7，8日，粤，将军潭边。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}